Running it I got several exceptions, but only one really **related to my problem**:

```shell
java.lang.reflect.InaccessibleObjectException: Unable to make private static java.lang.ClassLoader java.io.ObjectInputStream.latestUserDefinedLoader() accessible: module java.base does not &quot;opens java.io&quot; to unnamed module @50675690
